### Smart Task - WorkspaceController API Test
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Auth
@accessToken = REPLACE_ACCESS_TOKEN

### Dynamic IDs (update manually from previous responses)
@workspaceId = REPLACE_WORKSPACE_ID
@memberUserId = REPLACE_MEMBER_USER_ID
@pendingInviteUserId = REPLACE_PENDING_INVITE_USER_ID

### 1) Create workspace
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workspaces
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Smart Workspace A"
}

### 2) Get all workspaces (owner + participating)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/workspaces/my
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 3) Get workspace detail (includes myRole)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/workspaces/{{workspaceId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 4) Invite member (owner/admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workspaces/{{workspaceId}}/members/invite
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "member.test@example.com",
  "role": "member"
}

### 4.1) Invite member as admin (should become pending_owner_approval)
### Use an admin access token of this workspace to test
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workspaces/{{workspaceId}}/members/invite
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "member.pending@example.com",
  "role": "member"
}

### 5) List workspace members (owner/member/admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/workspaces/{{workspaceId}}/members
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 6) Update member role (owner only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/workspaces/{{workspaceId}}/members/{{memberUserId}}/role
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "admin"
}

### 6.1) Approve pending invitation (owner only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workspaces/{{workspaceId}}/members/{{pendingInviteUserId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 6.2) Reject pending invitation (owner only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/workspaces/{{workspaceId}}/members/{{pendingInviteUserId}}/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 7) Remove member (owner only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/workspaces/{{workspaceId}}/members/{{memberUserId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
